title: Contact
description: "Get in touch with The Traveling Times."
permalink: /contact/
---

<div class="container" style="padding-top: var(--space-12); padding-bottom: var(--space-16);">
  <div class="container--prose">

    <header style="margin-bottom: var(--space-10); padding-bottom: var(--space-6); border-bottom: 3px solid var(--color-ink);">
      <h1 style="font-family: var(--font-masthead); font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 3.815rem); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Contact</h1>
      <p style="font-size: var(--text-lg); color: var(--color-ink-muted); font-style: italic;">
        Questions, ideas, or just want to say hello?
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="article-body">

      <h2>Email</h2>
      <p>The best way to reach us is by email:</p>
      <p><a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a></p>

      <h2>Letters to the Editor</h2>
      <p>Have thoughts on something you read? We welcome reader correspondence. <a href="/submit/">Submit a letter</a> and it may be published in our Letters section.</p>

      <h2>Newsletter</h2>
      <p>Stay up to date with new articles delivered to your inbox. <a href="/newsletter/">Sign up for the newsletter</a> — it's free and you can unsubscribe anytime.</p>

      <h2>Corrections</h2>
      <p>If you spot an error in any article, please email us at <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a> with the article title and the correction. We take accuracy seriously and maintain a public <a href="/corrections/">corrections log</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
